trans-unit.source: Represents a single relationship between an object and a member.
trans-unit.target: Reprezentuje pojedynczy relacji między obiektem i element członkowski.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationshipService> is used by a serializer to announce that one property is related to a property on another object.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationshipService> jest używany przez element serializujący do anonsowania, że jedną właściwość jest powiązana z właściwością na inny obiekt.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship> represents a single relationship between an object and a member that <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationshipService> uses in its interactions with a serializer.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship> reprezentuje pojedynczy relacji między obiektem i element członkowski który <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationshipService> używa w jego interakcji z serializatora.

trans-unit.source: The object that owns <c>member</c>.
trans-unit.target: Obiekt, który jest właścicielem <c>elementu członkowskiego</c>.

trans-unit.source: The member which is to be related to <c>owner</c>.
trans-unit.target: Element członkowski, który ma być związane z <c>właściciela</c>.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicjuje nowe wystąpienie klasy <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> klasy.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="owner" /> or <paramref name="member" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="owner" /> lub <paramref name="member" /> jest <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: Represents the empty member relationship.
trans-unit.target: Reprezentuje relację pustego elementu członkowskiego.

trans-unit.source: This field is read-only.
trans-unit.target: To pole jest tylko do odczytu.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship> structure is empty if neither the owner nor the member is assigned.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship> struktura jest pusta, jeśli nie przypisano właściciela ani elementu członkowskiego.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> to compare with the current <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> Do porównania z bieżącym <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" />.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether two <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> instances are equal.
trans-unit.target: Określa, czy dwa <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> wystąpienia są takie same.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the specified <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> is equal to the current <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> Jeśli określony <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> jest taki sam, jak bieżący <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" />; w przeciwnym razie <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Returns the hash code for this instance.
trans-unit.target: Zwraca kod skrótu dla tego wystąpienia.

trans-unit.source: A hash code for the current <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" />.
trans-unit.target: Wartość skrótu dla bieżącego <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether this relationship is equal to the <see cref="F:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.Empty" /> relationship.
trans-unit.target: Pobiera wartość wskazującą, czy ta relacja jest równa <see cref="F:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.Empty" /> relacji.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if this relationship is equal to the <see cref="F:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.Empty" /> relationship; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> Jeśli ta relacja jest równa <see cref="F:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.Empty" /> relacji; w przeciwnym razie <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the related member.
trans-unit.target: Pobiera powiązany element członkowski.

trans-unit.source: The member that is passed in to the <see cref="M:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.#ctor(System.Object,System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor)" />.
trans-unit.target: Element członkowski, który jest przekazywany do <see cref="M:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.#ctor(System.Object,System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor)" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> structure that is to the left of the equality operator.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> Struktury z lewej strony operatora równości.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> structure that is to the right of the equality operator.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> Struktury z prawej strony operatora równości.

trans-unit.source: Tests whether two specified <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> structures are equivalent.
trans-unit.target: Sprawdza, czy dwa określone <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> struktury są równoważne.

trans-unit.source: This operator returns <see langword="true" /> if the two <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> structures are equal; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: Ten operator zwraca <see langword="true" /> Jeśli dwa <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> struktury są takie same; w przeciwnym razie <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The equivalent method for this operator is <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.Equals%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
trans-unit.target: Metoda równoważne tego operatora jest <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.Equals%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> structure that is to the left of the inequality operator.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> Struktury z lewej strony operator nierówności.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> structure that is to the right of the inequality operator.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> Strukturę po prawej stronie operator nierówności.

trans-unit.source: Tests whether two specified <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> structures are different.
trans-unit.target: Sprawdza, czy dwa określone <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> struktury są różne.

trans-unit.source: This operator returns <see langword="true" /> if the two <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> structures are different; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: Ten operator zwraca <see langword="true" /> Jeśli dwa <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> struktury są różne; w przeciwnym razie <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The equivalent method for this operator is <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.Equals%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
trans-unit.target: Metoda równoważne tego operatora jest <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.Equals%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the owning object.
trans-unit.target: Pobiera obiekt-właściciel.

trans-unit.source: The owning object that is passed in to the <see cref="M:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.#ctor(System.Object,System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor)" />.
trans-unit.target: Właścicielem obiektu, który jest przekazywany do <see cref="M:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.#ctor(System.Object,System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor)" />.
